    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay, that makes sense for the \"classic\" angle. to wrap this up for the pitch—if we were to expand this to a second persona that represents the \"new money\" or \"global elite\" segment, would you stick with that same European aesthetic, or would you suggest a different racial profile to capture that segment? what would the beauty standards be for that group?",
